{"tid":539374,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點算，女朋友身邊成班老姑婆fd","createTime":"2018-01-24T13:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:56:53.000Z","uid":36670,"like":79,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"843375e8cdb64cbfc8cbaddbd99cfa9cee1172e5","tid":539374,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"佢老尾，我同佢一齊左3年<br />\n都未去過旅行<br />\n次撚次都係班姑婆約佢去<br />\n去完就冇年假陪我<br />\n我同佢嘈，佢就話佢地約咗成班一齊去，要去埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多，逢係佢地齊人呢<br />\n就約咗我都會放我飛機<br />\n又係話難得齊人<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母，班老姑婆無仔要，緊係齊人架<br />\n<br />\n下下都係咁，我真係點算好<br />\n仲要唔知平時班老姑婆同佢講咗啲咩<br />\n佢又會信佢地先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你知㗎啦，女人去到廿五六七歲都無人要<br />\n一係就樣衰，一係就性格有問題<br />\n我真係驚班老姑婆搞到我同佢無得過正常拍拖生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母，學乜撚野人去旅行，儲錢買姑婆屋算啦屌</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"310ec7104850155ea06d8a04ca65858a4afe6670","tid":539374,"uid":1436,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你女朋友都做老姑婆"},{"pid":"c3085408acd7b4d51dfd98dc290b27a561b261d2","tid":539374,"uid":20448,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"岩啊 仲會嗌埋你條女落老蘭<br />\n過兩日你條女就會比南亞狗夾上房中出"},{"pid":"84de8359b2e3e083ad62dacca8be1df3c9bd3934","tid":539374,"uid":34023,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"25-6歲就變老姑婆<br />\n你都好快就變阿叔"},{"pid":"4ccaf27642b49685e62128799801afe10fe9ef9b","tid":539374,"uid":52227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"屌你早啲約佢買定機票嚕，我唔信你而家約佢年尾會話無假去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19333d2d00eb750ce35a7e48873a172e9c2ffd